{"tid":372245,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有無熟悉勞工法既巴絲幫下我","createTime":"2017-08-24T08:03:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T14:51:57.000Z","uid":90646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2b3348c646472716caeeaa874b4846dceb32de1d","tid":372245,"uid":90646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T08:03:31.000Z","msg":"前日因爲比航空公司取消左班飛機 因為個颱風啦<br />\n所以就番唔到香港 之後公司因為落左8號要番工<br />\n但飛機跟本仲未可以開始起飛番到去<br />\n但如果因爲天氣搞到飛機取消 番唔到果日既工<br />\n老闆係咪應該合理咁照扣我份糧同埋勤工？<br />\n<br />\n利申睇東方見到篇新聞唔清楚再開po問 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/24/160330_db77bf27fbd8fbda94b6ec1b2f0a2e70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F24%2F160330_db77bf27fbd8fbda94b6ec1b2f0a2e70.jpg&h=a0322051&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dfe5b082a968d13cc8c81ddfbe89f527d57764d7","tid":372245,"uid":90646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T08:07:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無知一問"},{"pid":"d804b5e9d3371149a04f852d86b9c84c5369bd07","tid":372245,"uid":81335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T08:13:50.000Z","msg":"唔lm"},{"pid":"04b8e47933535eb7c2f2d209c7d5d7e042bfe718","tid":372245,"uid":126843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T08:15:59.000Z","msg":"我都想知留名"},{"pid":"957d93bd5b99bbc1a9b429a593443bb442f90133","tid":372245,"uid":90646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T08:22:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔lm</blockquote><br />\n唔小心出賣左人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d797c823639a65d68e8ce532b2d454f111f707f6","tid":372245,"uid":90646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T08:26:28.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"f3259009d7426c1ab7d7f370de294159f98710ec","tid":372245,"uid":51387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T08:29:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前日因爲比航空公司取消左班飛機 因為個颱風啦<br />\n所以就番唔到香港 之後公司因為落左8號要番工<br />\n但飛機跟本仲未可以開始起飛番到去<br />\n但如果因爲天氣搞到飛機取消 番唔到果日既工<br />\n老闆係咪應該合理咁照扣我份糧同埋勤工？<br />\n<br />\n利申睇東方見到篇新聞唔清楚再開po問 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/24/160330_db77bf27fbd8fbda94b6ec1b2f0a2e70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F24%2F160330_db77bf27fbd8fbda94b6ec1b2f0a2e70.jpg&h=a0322051&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家個僱主炒你定扣1日糧? 話你曠工炒你的話就係無理解僱. 如果係缺勤扣1日人工就屬合理. <br />\n<br />\n至於勤工, 呢類額外收入勞工例唔會保障到你嘅."},{"pid":"bf8cfcff9c544a6ab7d9d38a7116059a986529c9","tid":372245,"uid":90646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T08:31:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>前日因爲比航空公司取消左班飛機 因為個颱風啦<br />\n所以就番唔到香港 之後公司因為落左8號要番工<br />\n但飛機跟本仲未可以開始起飛番到去<br />\n但如果因爲天氣搞到飛機取消 番唔到果日既工<br />\n老闆係咪應該合理咁照扣我份糧同埋勤工？<br />\n<br />\n利申睇東方見到篇新聞唔清楚再開po問 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/24/160330_db77bf27fbd8fbda94b6ec1b2f0a2e70.j.pg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F24%2F160330_db77bf27fbd8fbda94b6ec1b2f0a2e70.j.pg&h=e76e0e8f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家個僱主炒你定扣1日糧? 話你曠工炒你的話就係無理解僱. 如果係缺勤扣1日人工就屬合理. <br />\n<br />\n至於勤工, 呢類額外收入勞工例唔會保障到你嘅.</blockquote><br />\n扣勤工同埋糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09bf5f553267ed295b321085a90f39213e939ced","tid":372245,"uid":770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T08:35:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"90e7b7914c38ff87c119c53fba9dde8cf47ca4b5","tid":372245,"uid":51387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T08:37:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n扣勤工同埋糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你確實係缺勤1個工作天, 扣你1日糧係合法的(唔合情的部份係理論上你就算係返都只係返幾個鐘). <br />\n<br />\n咁既然係缺勤, 呢個月當然冇勤工."},{"pid":"b56187e9b8178f62f3a4b71224a3f391bf2f733f","tid":372245,"uid":770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T08:40:17.000Z","msg":"樓主假膠黎"},{"pid":"f5eca89312f899c4f55161ca10ec9ae08358b650","tid":372245,"uid":36359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T08:47:46.000Z","msg":"勤工屬於獎金 ，個玩法係你老細話哂事，勞工法例係唔會理。除非你本身份合約上面寫明個玩法而宜家又違反先有得拗。<br />\n<br />\n扣糧理論上佢最多只可以按比例扣你缺勤既時間。但呢度有灰色地帶，要睇番你既合約有冇訂明每日既工作時間，如果冇基本上又係任佢講。<br />\n<br />\n其實香港地勞工法唔係保障勞工，勸你都係慳番啖氣，得閒搵過份好過"},{"pid":"ee1d75e05ce0c7cca3f09baa8b0ab510cdae0dab","tid":372245,"uid":51387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T08:50:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n其實香港地勞工法唔係保障勞工，勸你都係慳番啖氣，得閒搵過份好過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n基本上你搵勞工處, 勞工處係會企喺僱主方奚落你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25eead6dfd1475bf3ec7c8cc21a7f3e7b68206e7","tid":372245,"uid":90646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T08:58:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主假膠黎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36793cf0796f21e2acfcf8250fd9463e851b050c","tid":372245,"uid":90646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T08:58:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n其實香港地勞工法唔係保障勞工，勸你都係慳番啖氣，得閒搵過份好過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n基本上你搵勞工處, 勞工處係會企喺僱主方奚落你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我做埋今個月唔做啦依份工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\